have been conversations in the Moncler building, but it sounds like they we=
re largely speculative. (Representatives for both companies said they don=
=E2=80=99t comment on rumors.)

Some on the Burberry side wonder if this was just bankers causing trouble a=
nd trying to spark some deal heat=E2=80=94there has long been an M&A premiu=
m on the stock=E2=80=94or if some other force (an influential shareholder, =
