lf. Alas, the stock dipped back down after investors raised an eyebrow abou=
t the rumor. <br/><br/>I did a little recon, myself, too. And after talking=
 to people on
both sides, I confirmed that the deal chatter is far,<i> far </i>from real.=
 There <i>have</i> been conversations in the Moncler building, but it sound=
