teen</i>. The company
line, I=E2=80=99m told, is that costs are outpacing revenue, and that from =
now on there may be a greater focus on the agency work and perhaps commerce=
=E2=80=94although I hear there are also plans to phase out Highsnobiety HS0=
5, the in-house label, even though they will continue to produce other type=
s of product.<br/><br/>As for the print product, for which Bennett won a Na=
