 resources=E2=80=9D as they continue =E2=80=9Cstreamlining our global struc=
ture to more closely align with the shifting industry as well as internal n=
eeds.=E2=80=9D Most importantly, though, they wanted me to know that the ed=
itorial vision for the company=E2=80=94and the business model=E2=80=94=E2=
=80=9Cremain unchanged by any of these measures.=E2=80=9D<br/><br/>Reading =
between the lines, my educated guess is that layoffs were likely a mandate =
from the powers that be at Zalando to put a tourniquet around the business.=
